cross: Paphiopedilum Hsinying Majakun x Paphiopedilum Hsinying Jewel

measurements.description: One flower on one 22-cm inflorescence on a single growth plant; dorsal sepal white striped bright green; synsepal light green striped bright green; petals hirsute, ivory striped green, fading distally, translucent stripe lower half, warts upper half; pouch pale green, veined green; staminode pale green tessellated dark green centrally; substance firm; texture waxy.
